## Setup R in CLUSTER Computer 
# Need to install R packages before running the scripts
# Follow these commands to install them
~~
mkdir ~/R_LIBS
ml r-4.4.1-gcc-12.2.0-x6ecfp6 

Rscript install.R
~~

# Then, we can run rscripts (after loading the module)
# by simply typing:
# Rscrip script_name.R

# or to store output:
# Rscript script_name.R > logs/log_file.out 2>&1 &
